</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>2021 Apple App Store Awards 公佈，最佳手遊：LoL : Wild Rift、MARVEL 未來革命</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/02/2021-app-store-awards/mobile-phone/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=2021-app-store-awards</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Lawton]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 02 Dec 2021 08:01:17 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[iOS App]]></category><category><![CDATA[iPad App]]></category><category><![CDATA[手提電話]]></category><category><![CDATA[App Store Awards]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1073834</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>Apple 今日公佈 App Store Awards 2021，包括全球性的最佳手機、平板、電腦 App 與 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Apple 今日公佈 App Store Awards 2021，包括全球性的最佳手機、平板、電腦 App 與遊戲的得獎作品，以及地域性的最佳 App、遊戲獎項。當中兒童向虛擬模擬經營平台《Toca Life World》成為全球年度 App 大獎，而《LoL》iPhone 版、《Marvel Future Revolution》iPad 版榮獲全球性手機、平板遊戲大獎。香港方面，最多人下載的免費 App 為《安心出行》，值得關注的是通訊軟件 Signal 成為第二最多人下載的 iPhone App，翻牆工具 Shadowrocket 成為最多人購買的付費 iPhone App，反映香港人對於資訊安全的需求愈來愈大。</p><h2>2021 App Store Award 全球性得獎名單</h2><h2>應用程式類</h2><p>iPhone App of the Year: Toca Life World, 製作商：Toca Boca</p><p>iPad App of the Year: LumaFusion, 製作商：LumaTouch</p><p>Mac App of the Year: Craft, 製作商：Luki Labs Limited</p><p>Apple TV App of the Year: DAZN, 製作商：DAZN Group</p><p>Apple Watch App of the Year: Carrot Weather, 製作商：Grailr</p><h2>遊戲類</h2><p>iPhone Game of the Year: 「League of Legends: Wild Rift《英雄聯盟：激鬥峽谷》」 製作商：Riot Games</p><p>iPad Game of the Year: 「MARVEL Future Revolution《MARVEL 未來革命》,」 製作商：Netmarble Corporation</p><p>Mac Game of the Year: 「Myst,」 製作商：Cyan</p><p>Apple TV Game of the Year: 「Space Marshals 3,」 製作商：Pixelbite</p><p>Apple Arcade Game of the Year: 「Fantasian,」 製作商：Mistwalker</p><p>今年 iPhone App of the Year 得獎者為 Toca Life World，這款 App 是以兒童為對象的模擬經營遊戲，同「元宇宙」概念也搭上關係。遊戲玩家多為小學生，遊戲世界裡面有一張大地圖，玩家自製一個角色，在空地上建築甜品店、戲院等，更可直接進入這些建築物。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/TocaLife_World_GameArt.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1073836" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/TocaLife_World_GameArt-694x425.png" alt="" width="694" height="425" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/TocaLife_World_GameArt-694x425.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/TocaLife_World_GameArt-1280x785.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/TocaLife_World_GameArt-768x471.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/TocaLife_World_GameArt-1536x941.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/TocaLife_World_GameArt-2048x1255.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/TocaLife_World_GameArt.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Apple_App-Store-Awards-2021_Toca-Boca_12022021_screen.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1073837" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Apple_App-Store-Awards-2021_Toca-Boca_12022021_screen-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Apple_App-Store-Awards-2021_Toca-Boca_12022021_screen-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Apple_App-Store-Awards-2021_Toca-Boca_12022021_screen-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Apple_App-Store-Awards-2021_Toca-Boca_12022021_screen-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Apple_App-Store-Awards-2021_Toca-Boca_12022021_screen-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Apple_App-Store-Awards-2021_Toca-Boca_12022021_screen-2048x1152.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Apple_App-Store-Awards-2021_Toca-Boca_12022021_screen.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>而 iPhone 年度遊戲 iPhone Game of the Year，就由《League of Legends: Wild Rift》（英雄聯盟：激鬥峽谷）奪得。本作為 MOBA 多人網上戰鬥競技場遊戲，為同名電腦版的手機作品，遊戲裡用家要集結隊友摧毀敵方基地。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Apple_App-Store-Awards-2021_League-of-Legends-WildRift_12022021_screen.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1073838" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Apple_App-Store-Awards-2021_League-of-Legends-WildRift_12022021_screen-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Apple_App-Store-Awards-2021_League-of-Legends-WildRift_12022021_screen-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Apple_App-Store-Awards-2021_League-of-Legends-WildRift_12022021_screen-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Apple_App-Store-Awards-2021_League-of-Legends-WildRift_12022021_screen-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Apple_App-Store-Awards-2021_League-of-Legends-WildRift_12022021_screen-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Apple_App-Store-Awards-2021_League-of-Legends-WildRift_12022021_screen-2048x1152.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Apple_App-Store-Awards-2021_League-of-Legends-WildRift_12022021_screen.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-15.43.39.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1073852" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-15.43.39-694x527.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="527" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-15.43.39-694x527.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-15.43.39-1185x900.jpg 1185w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-15.43.39-768x583.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-15.43.39.jpg 1235w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>至於 iPad App of the Year 年度大獎得獎者為 LumaFusion。此 App 為影片剪輯工具，可在同一介面下匯入多軌影片同時編輯，可將一般平凡影片剪輯成專業級作品。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/iPadPro-iPhone-combo-2 副本.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1073841" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/iPadPro-iPhone-combo-2 副本-694x528.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="528" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/iPadPro-iPhone-combo-2 副本-694x528.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/iPadPro-iPhone-combo-2 副本-1182x900.jpg 1182w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/iPadPro-iPhone-combo-2 副本-768x585.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/iPadPro-iPhone-combo-2 副本-1536x1169.jpg 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/iPadPro-iPhone-combo-2 副本.jpg 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>而 iPad Game of the Year 大獎的得主為《MARVEL Future Revolution》，以漫威英雄作為主題，以開放世界動作 RPG 吸引玩家。玩家會成為新組成的超級英雄團隊的特工，抵擋來自超級反派的攻擊。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-15.43.51-1.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1073854" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-15.43.51-1-529x580.jpg" alt="" width="529" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-15.43.51-1-529x580.jpg 529w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-15.43.51-1-768x842.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-15.43.51-1.jpg 818w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 529px" /></a><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Apple_App-Store-Awards-2021_Marvel-Future-Revolution_12022021_screen.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1073843" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Apple_App-Store-Awards-2021_Marvel-Future-Revolution_12022021_screen-694x562.png" alt="" width="694" height="562" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Apple_App-Store-Awards-2021_Marvel-Future-Revolution_12022021_screen-694x562.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Apple_App-Store-Awards-2021_Marvel-Future-Revolution_12022021_screen-1112x900.png 1112w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Apple_App-Store-Awards-2021_Marvel-Future-Revolution_12022021_screen-768x621.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Apple_App-Store-Awards-2021_Marvel-Future-Revolution_12022021_screen-1536x1243.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Apple_App-Store-Awards-2021_Marvel-Future-Revolution_12022021_screen-2048x1657.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/Apple_App-Store-Awards-2021_Marvel-Future-Revolution_12022021_screen.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>香港 2021 App Store Award 得獎名單</h2><p>Apple 同日亦公佈了香港地區 10 大付費、免費的 iPhone、iPad 應用程式與遊戲。當中成為免費應用程式之冠是《安心出行》，而通訊軟件 Signal 成為了排行第 2 之 10 大免費 iPhone App。除了知名應用程式外，醫健通、八達通、MeWe 等入榜，代表市民陸續在 2021 年更活用智能化工具，與網民從 FB 出走到 MeWe 的現象。而政府積極推廣的「智方便 iAM Smart」則只排第 9。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-15.38.16.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1073844" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-15.38.16-694x475.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="475" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-15.38.16-694x475.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-15.38.16.jpg 748w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>而付費軟件方面，最多人願意付費購買的為有翻牆功能的資訊保安工具 Shadowrocket。另外用戶對於生產力工具仍然有強大需求，GoodNotes 5、Notability、CamScanner 都有上榜。特別注意是排行第 2 的「Forest」屬於專注軟件，它要求用家不滑手機，專心去做目前工作與學習，不滑手機反而能獲得獎勵，幫助森林成長。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-15.39.05.jpg"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1073845" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-15.39.05-694x437.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="437" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-15.39.05-694x437.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-15.39.05-768x484.jpg 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/螢幕截圖-2021-12-02-15.39.05.jpg 1060w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><h2>香港 10 大付費 iPhone Apps</h2><p>1. Shadowrocket</p><p>2. Forest &#8211; Your Focus Motivation</p><p>3. GoodNotes 5</p><p>4. AutoSleep Track Sleep on Watch</p><p>5. TouchRetouch</p><p>6. iSafe Pro</p><p>7. Notability</p><p>8. Procreate Pocket</p><p>9. MOODA</p><p>10. CamScanner + OCR Scanner</p><h2>香港 10 大免費 iPhone Apps</h2><p>1. LeaveHomeSafe 安心出行</p><p>2. Signal &#8211; Private Messenger</p><p>3. WhatsApp Messenger</p><p>4. BOCHK 中銀香港</p><p>5. 醫健通 eHealth</p><p>6. Octopus 八達通</p><p>7. YouTube: Watch, Listen, Stream</p><p>8. MeWe Network</p><p>9. 智方便 iAM Smart</p><p>10. Instagram</p><h2>香港 10 大付費 iPhone Games<span class="Apple-converted-space"> </span></h2><p>1. Minecraft</p><p>2. Plague Inc.</p><p>3. 三國志天下布武</p><p>4. Football Manager 2021 Mobile</p><p>5. Muse Dash 喵斯快跑-跑酷游戏</p><p>6. Dungeon Village 2</p><p>7. Forest Camp Story</p><p>8. Boxing Gym Story</p><p>9. Rebel Inc.</p><p>10. Hot Springs Story2</p><h2>香港 10 大免費 iPhone Games</h2><p>1. Coin Master</p><p>2. League of Legends: Wild Rift</p><p>3. Among Us!</p><p>4. 新射鵰群俠傳之鐵血丹心</p><p>5. 聖鬥士星矢:正義傳說</p><p>6. Project Makeover</p><p>7. PUBG MOBILE: RESISTANCE</p><p>8. 開心鬥一番-麻雀、啤牌任你玩</p><p>9. 放置神將 &#8211; 高福利卡牌手遊</p><p>10. Roblox</p><h2>香港 10 大付費 iPad Apps</h2><p>1. GoodNotes 5</p><p>2. Procreate</p><p>3. Notability</p><p>4. Shadowrocket</p><p>5. Messaging for WhatsApp on iPad</p><p>6. Duet Display</p><p>7. LumaFusion</p><p>8. Nomad Sculpt</p><p>9. Forest &#8211; Your Focus Motivation</p><p>10. Affinity Photo</p><h2>香港 10 大免費 iPad Apps</h2><p>1. YouTube</p><p>2. ZOOM Cloud Meetings</p><p>3. Google Chrome</p><p>4. Netflix</p><p>5. ViuTV</p><p>6. Gmail &#8211; Email by Google</p><p>7. Google Drive</p><p>8. Google Classroom</p><p>9. Microsoft Word</p><p>10. Calculator for iPad +</p><h2>香港 10 大付費 iPad Games</h2><p>1. Minecraft</p><p>2. Plague Inc.</p><p>3. Muse Dash 喵斯快跑-跑酷游戏</p><p>4. Football Manager 2021 Touch</p><p>5. Divinity &#8211; Original Sin 2</p><p>6. Bloons TD 6</p><p>7. Lanota</p><p>8. RFS &#8211; Real Flight Simulator</p><p>9. Mini Metro</p><p>10. 三國志天下布武</p><h2>香港 10 大免費 iPad Games</h2><p>1. Among Us!</p><p>2. Roblox</p><p>3. PUBG MOBILE: RESISTANCE</p><p>4. Merge Snake!</p><p>5. Mini World: CREATA</p><p>6. Genshin Impact</p><p>7. Garena 傳說對決:五週年版本</p><p>8. Coin Master</p><p>9. Brawl Stars</p><p>10. Tiles Hop &#8211; EDM Rush</p><p>資料來源：Apple</p></p><div class="feedflare">
