</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>Forza Horizon 5 改裝「金正恩」車款，玩家即被封帳至 9999 年</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2021/12/01/player-banned-from-forza-horizon-5-for-8000-years-for-portraying-kim-jong-un-in-a-car/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=player-banned-from-forza-horizon-5-for-8000-years-for-portraying-kim-jong-un-in-a-car</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Miranda]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Wed, 01 Dec 2021 12:33:04 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[Forza Horizon 5]]></category><category><![CDATA[帳號被封]]></category><category><![CDATA[金正恩]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1073719</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>帳號被封日前上架的遊戲《極限競速，地平線 5》（Forza Horizon 5）獲得一眾系列粉絲好評，除了可設 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-weight: 400;">帳號被封日前上架的遊戲《極限競速，地平線 5》（Forza Horizon 5）獲得一眾系列粉絲好評，除了可設計車輛塗裝外更可與玩家分享並透過社群創作功能下載。但最近就有一名玩家因以「金正恩」頭像設計塗裝被官方 Ban 帳，該帳號封鎖的停權時間直到西元 9999 年 12 月 31 日才能解鎖。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1073720" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/C56E912B-2625-4E4E-AD88-ABEC5A8DA9CC-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/C56E912B-2625-4E4E-AD88-ABEC5A8DA9CC-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/C56E912B-2625-4E4E-AD88-ABEC5A8DA9CC-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/C56E912B-2625-4E4E-AD88-ABEC5A8DA9CC-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/C56E912B-2625-4E4E-AD88-ABEC5A8DA9CC-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/C56E912B-2625-4E4E-AD88-ABEC5A8DA9CC.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">玩家「AllThingsRacing」近日在討論區 Reddit 發表帖文，表示他有一位朋友因在遊戲中設計了以北韓領導人金正恩取代肯德基上校的 KFC 主題造型的車輛塗裝而被 Ban 8000 年。車身上可見北韓首都平壤（Pyongyang）字樣、模仿 NIKE 改成「NUKE」（核彈）的商標，以及「#SendNukes」Hashtag 等。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1073721" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/CDAB3F67-FC0F-4FCD-8776-4FE87577F2D4-694x390.png" alt="" width="694" height="390" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/CDAB3F67-FC0F-4FCD-8776-4FE87577F2D4-694x390.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/CDAB3F67-FC0F-4FCD-8776-4FE87577F2D4-1280x720.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/CDAB3F67-FC0F-4FCD-8776-4FE87577F2D4-768x432.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/CDAB3F67-FC0F-4FCD-8776-4FE87577F2D4-1536x864.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/CDAB3F67-FC0F-4FCD-8776-4FE87577F2D4.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">根據 AllThingsRacin 所提供的截圖顯示，他的朋友在無預警下收到官方的帳號停權懲罰，帳號封鎖的停權時間直到西元 9999 年 12 月 31 日才能解鎖。事件引發網民熱烈討論，有不少玩家認為這項懲處過於荒謬，只是改造車輛造型，算不上是需要封鎖 8,000 年的違規事項；但亦有指若不做出懲處，是次「惡搞」可能會為遊戲商股東與合作夥伴帶來一些麻煩。</span></p><p><img loading="lazy" class="alignnone size-medium wp-image-1073722" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/90B935B4-F933-416D-9792-B47875CDD6CC-694x223.png" alt="" width="694" height="223" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/90B935B4-F933-416D-9792-B47875CDD6CC-694x223.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/90B935B4-F933-416D-9792-B47875CDD6CC-768x247.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2021/12/90B935B4-F933-416D-9792-B47875CDD6CC.png 803w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">資料來源：<a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/forza/comments/r4biyx/my_friend_got_an_8000_year_ban/?sort=qa">Reddit</a></span></p><p><span style="font-weight: 400;">&#8212; unwire.hk Mewe 專頁 :</span> <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><span style="font-weight: 400;">https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</span></a></p></p><di